From 04f66ab64ae9abbfd1db7dc62c65fb1e2dbd2498 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Glen Kirkham <Glenkirkham@gmail.com>
Date: Sun, 22 Mar 2026 22:21:36 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] feat(flowerhub-ops): add FlowerHub 3D Ops view wired to
 real staffroom data
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

New route at /flowerhub shows a 4-panel ops dashboard reading directly
from /Users/glenkirkham/flowerhub-staffroom-data/data/:

Panels:
- Active Agents    ← active_tasks.json (LIVE/STALE/MISSING, 10m threshold)
- Sprint Board     ← OFFICE-BOARD.md active sprint cards
- Task Queue       ← TASK-BOARD.md WIP=1 card queue
- Inbox Queue      ← inbox_queue.json, needs-human items highlighted

Features:
- Per-source LIVE/STALE/MISSING badge + "updated X ago" timestamp
- Manual refresh button + 60s auto-refresh countdown
- Priority strip from Office Board objective
- Agent roles from Agent Route Map shown under each agent card
- 30s server-side in-memory cache; FLOWERHUB_DATA_DIR env var for portability
- No changes to existing /office, /agents, or any existing scene

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
